{"tid":1655572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"也許 聞一多","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T07:53:33.000Z","uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7b400684c99f6096677780001e3d27263506c4","tid":1655572,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"也許你真是哭得太累，<br />\n<br />\n也許，也許你要睡一睡，<br />\n<br />\n那麼叫夜鷹不要咳嗽，<br />\n<br />\n蛙不要號，蝙蝠不要飛；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不許陽光撥你的眼簾，<br />\n<br />\n不許清風刷上你的眉，<br />\n<br />\n無論誰都不能驚醒你，<br />\n<br />\n撐一傘松陰庇護你睡；<br />\n<br />\n也許你聽這蚯蚓翻泥，<br />\n<br />\n聽這小草的根鬚吸水，<br />\n<br />\n也許你聽這般的音樂，<br />\n<br />\n比那咒罵的人聲更美；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那麼你先把眼皮閉緊，<br />\n<br />\n我就讓你睡，我讓你睡，<br />\n<br />\n我把黃土輕輕蓋著你，<br />\n<br />\n我叫紙錢兒緩緩的飛。"},{"pid":"989b38d64c0a0caf6ced3abd725044356404cf7b","tid":1655572,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26625c61f38ab48f614380d48944ce3b679560c7","tid":1655572,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F0xPRWvitlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF0xPRWvitlg&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=e63f1f9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F0xPRWvitlg</a>"}]}